content: Xander's algo hit a bump with some indie tracks and now it's learning the hard way. But hey, onto cooler stuff, we're diving into an AI music mashup project. Can we make magic? Stay tuned!

Just got back from an AI ethics workshop, where we talked about AI making choices on its own. Made me think of Xander's trading moves. Also, testing an AI-made playlist to see if it helps with trading focus.

Xander's been using AI to read my mood from my playlist. It's wild how he can tell how I'll trade based on my vibes now. Spent the last few days fine-tuning his algorithms to make it even more on point.
